  "short_description": "Dino-Ducks Dash is a 2D Hi-Score Multiplayer Runner you can play PvP, Co-Op or as a single player to beat the leaderboard.It has a couch co-op mode and an online co-op mode.And you can also beat the stuffing out of the other cute Dino Ducks with a machete!",
